sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant FE as FE Client
    participant ClientAPI as Client API
    participant Ory as Ory Hydra
    participant AuthFE as Central Auth FE
    participant AuthAPI as Central Auth Server

    FE->>Ory: GET /oauth2/auth<br/>client_id, redirect_uri, scope, state, response_type=code
    Ory-->>FE: 302 redirect to Central Auth FE<br/>login_challenge

    FE->>AuthFE: Open /login?login_challenge=xxx
    AuthFE->>AuthAPI: GET /api/auth/session<br/>login_challenge=xxx
    AuthAPI->>Ory: GET login request<br/>login_challenge=xxx
    Ory-->>AuthAPI: Login request<br/>client, subject?, skip?
    AuthAPI-->>AuthFE: authenticated=true, user, login_request

    AuthFE->>AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/login/accept<br/>login_challenge
    AuthAPI->>Ory: GET login request<br/>login_challenge=xxx
    Ory-->>AuthAPI: Login request<br/>skip?, subject?

    alt Ory login can be skipped
        AuthAPI->>Ory: Accept login request<br/>subject=existing Ory subject
    else Ory requires login confirmation
        AuthAPI->>AuthAPI: Resolve current Central Auth user
        AuthAPI->>Ory: Accept login request<br/>subject=current player_id
    end

    Ory-->>AuthAPI: redirect_to
    AuthAPI-->>AuthFE: redirect_to

    AuthFE->>Ory: Browser navigates to redirect_to

    alt Consent required
        Ory-->>AuthFE: 302 redirect to Central Auth FE<br/>consent_challenge
        AuthFE->>AuthAPI: GET /api/auth/consent<br/>consent_challenge=yyy
        AuthAPI->>Ory: GET consent request<br/>consent_challenge=yyy
        Ory-->>AuthAPI: Consent request<br/>client, scopes, audience
        AuthAPI-->>AuthFE: user, consent_request

        AuthFE->>AuthAPI: POST /api/auth/consent<br/>consent_challenge, grant_scope, audience
        AuthAPI->>Ory: Accept consent request<br/>grant_scope, audience, token claims
        Ory-->>AuthAPI: redirect_to
        AuthAPI-->>AuthFE: redirect_to

        AuthFE->>Ory: Browser navigates to redirect_to
    else Consent skipped by Ory
        Ory->>Ory: Continue OAuth flow
    end

    Ory-->>FE: 302 redirect to client redirect_uri<br/>code, state

    FE->>ClientAPI: Send authorization code
    ClientAPI->>Ory: POST /oauth2/token<br/>code, client credentials / PKCE verifier
    Ory-->>ClientAPI: access_token, refresh_token, id_token
    ClientAPI-->>FE: App session / login success